Greetings.
You are receiving this email because your company, in some capacity, is a partner with Chosen Payments in our pursuit of the hospitality merchant community, and we believe that you ought to be included in this discovery process.
Attached is a document that was generated as a result of our discussions with enterprise properties in the casino/resort space. We have been seeking a "universal" solution to support our clients and the response from the marketplace has been, well, disappointing. One of our largest and most respected gaming/resort clients, who we have provided service to for more than seven years ... and who operate properties around the globe ... developed this integration requirement concept document, and it is my expectation that we can develop an integration of this nature through our CardConnect partnership.
Chosen Payments chose CardConnect for their technology, including the CardPointe tools, and the belief that innovation was a core principle of the organization. My intention is to use this initial email as an opportunity to assess whether or not the reality of this concept is viable. I would like to do an initial conference call sometime next week with the goal of organizing a meeting between key parties to discuss this in person. I am open to traveling to Chicago, Denver, or any other location, in order to meet with each of you and determine the best and fastest way to get this done.
I respectfully request that you share this document with the appropriate person within your organization who has the vision and authority to see this project to fruition.
Please reach out to me with your thoughts.
